CROSS JOIN jsonb_array_elements(
    '[{"start":0,"end":4.88,"text":"Today I''m going to show you exactly how to use Gmail even if you''re a complete beginner."},{"start":4.88,"end":10.72,"text":"Let''s jump in. So first we''re going to just head over to mail.google.com and it''s going to open up"},{"start":10.72,"end":18,"text":"your Gmail account and Gmail has become wildly popular over the last few years and if you have"},{"start":18,"end":23.84,"text":"any Google account you have a corresponding Gmail account. So first let''s talk about composing emails"},{"start":23.92,"end":30.16,"text":"probably the the main feature that you''re looking for in Gmail. So when you''re on this home screen"},{"start":30.16,"end":35.6,"text":"we''re just going to head over to the compose button real big button over here and you click on that"},{"start":35.6,"end":42.4,"text":"it''ll open up a window down here in the corner and you can continue to scroll through your emails"},{"start":42.4,"end":48.8,"text":"this way while you have this open minimize it if you need to or you can expand it so that it''s more"},{"start":48.88,"end":55.2,"text":"of a full screen here. So first you just want to add your two box and let''s say I just want to send"},{"start":55.2,"end":62.4,"text":"an email to myself you see when I do that it auto populates to if you have any accounts already"},{"start":62.4,"end":70.24,"text":"in your system and then you can add your subject and then your body of your message here. Now down"},{"start":70.24,"end":75.04,"text":"here you can change some functions if you''re familiar with any sort of word processing"},{"start":75.04,"end":80.56,"text":"software you can change your fonts you can you know make it bold or italics profile you"},{"start":80.56,"end":85.44,"text":"do bullets and lists I mean you could really format the email exactly how you want in there."},{"start":85.44,"end":90.16,"text":"The other thing I''ll show you while we''re in here is you could click on the little paper clip"},{"start":90.8,"end":96.72,"text":"you click on that and you could add an attachment if there''s a document or something that you want"},{"start":96.72,"end":104.64,"text":"to attach to there you can add that so let''s say I want to attach that image and it will"},{"start":104.64,"end":111.44,"text":"attach that image to the email as long as it''s under a certain size okay and another option"},{"start":111.44,"end":118.64,"text":"that you may need is you click on the little pen tool and you could insert a signature and so this"},{"start":118.64,"end":125.04,"text":"is a default closing to your email if you don''t have any signatures in here you click on manage"},{"start":125.04,"end":130.08,"text":"signatures and you''ll only have to set this up once and then you''ll be able to use it each time"},{"start":130.08,"end":135.2,"text":"you do this so we''re just going to scrunch that down here so we can see what else is on the screen"},{"start":136,"end":142.8,"text":"and it is taking us into our settings here and then when you scroll down through here you''ll see"},{"start":142.8,"end":148.32,"text":"signature so that you can create a new one and you could just name this because you''re going to have"},{"start":148.32,"end":152.56,"text":"several different signatures you could have personal you could have business you could have"},{"start":152.56,"end":157.04,"text":"whatever you want so I''m just going to do I''m going to call this primary and we''re going to"},{"start":157.04,"end":163.28,"text":"click create and then here you just type what you want that signature to look like so you click in"},{"start":163.28,"end":172.08,"text":"here and you go andy canode I''ll do a little quote have a great day and then you can list your phone"},{"start":172.96,"end":178.24,"text":"and your email or whatever you want and then we''re just going to minimize this so we can see"},{"start":178.24,"end":183.76,"text":"everything that''s in there and once that''s done then you have that signature and you can see you"},{"start":183.76,"end":189.04,"text":"could just keep creating additional you create another one and do business but once you have"},{"start":189.04,"end":195.52,"text":"those created they''re in there and then you could set a default down below here so for new emails"},{"start":195.52,"end":201.36,"text":"going out let''s say I want to use my primary you can always change that but that is just for"},{"start":201.36,"end":206.72,"text":"the sake of being able to have that available and then what''s key is if you do anything in the"},{"start":206.72,"end":211.68,"text":"settings you want to make sure you scroll down to the bottom click on save changes and it''ll take"},{"start":211.68,"end":216.8,"text":"you back to the main screen we''re just going to reopen our email that we were creating here now"},{"start":216.8,"end":221.12,"text":"once we''ve made that change since we already had this email open this is a good opportunity to show"},{"start":221.12,"end":226.8,"text":"you something else that happens here is we haven''t sent this email yet so we''ve created this what"},{"start":226.8,"end":232.24,"text":"we''re going to do is we''re going to click the x so we''re just going to close out of that okay now"},{"start":232.24,"end":238.4,"text":"you could see over here on the side we have all our navigation boxes that we''re looking at inboxes"},{"start":238.4,"end":245.2,"text":"our primary here but then down in drafts is that email that we just created and you see it says in"},{"start":245.2,"end":250.64,"text":"red right real big right here draft so that means this has not been sent this is just a draft and"},{"start":250.64,"end":255.92,"text":"if you click on that it''ll allow you to go back in here and start editing now we''ve gone out of it"},{"start":255.92,"end":260.96,"text":"and we''ve come back in we can click on the signatures and you see it populates with our"},{"start":261.04,"end":266.96,"text":"additional signatures here click on primary and you see it lists that down here as our signature"},{"start":266.96,"end":271.12,"text":"and you can make adjustments maybe in this one i don''t want to include the phone number"},{"start":271.12,"end":276.88,"text":"so i can make that adjustment that didn''t change the format of the signature it just changed it in"},{"start":276.88,"end":282.64,"text":"this email and you can continue typing and editing okay and once you have the email exactly the way"},{"start":282.64,"end":288.88,"text":"you want it all you do is you can go down here and click send or to the right you see little"},{"start":288.88,"end":294.08,"text":"arrows you click on that arrow and you could schedule to send that email so let''s say i want"},{"start":294.08,"end":301.12,"text":"to schedule it to send tomorrow morning and now it won''t send right now it''ll send it tomorrow"},{"start":301.12,"end":304.64,"text":"morning which is kind of a nice feature so let''s go back into that email i''m going to show you"},{"start":304.64,"end":309.92,"text":"another situation here what a lot of people don''t know is you can actually undo a send or pull an"},{"start":309.92,"end":314.56,"text":"email back before it actually goes out and i''ll show you how to do this let''s say we have the"},{"start":314.56,"end":320.48,"text":"email typed up we click on send which is going to send it immediately you can see a pop up here"},{"start":320.48,"end":328,"text":"and it says message sent and undo if we click that undo it brings it back in here and that message"},{"start":328,"end":333.36,"text":"never was sent it''s a nice feature if you send an email and immediately realize that there was a"},{"start":333.36,"end":338.88,"text":"spelling error or you forgot to attach that file we''ve all done that a hundred times you have that"},{"start":338.88,"end":345.04,"text":"option to undo that it''s only for a few seconds so let''s say i didn''t want to send that attachment"},{"start":345.04,"end":351.92,"text":"so we could click that x get rid of the attachment and then click send and you can see message sent"},{"start":351.92,"end":357.68,"text":"and this will disappear after a few seconds and that means the message has fully gone through now"},{"start":357.68,"end":363.92,"text":"you can adjust that time window up to 30 seconds i''ll show you how to do that when you go into your"},{"start":363.92,"end":368.72,"text":"when you''re looking at the main screen here up in the corner you can see a little gear icon"},{"start":368.72,"end":374.48,"text":"that''s your settings so we''re going to open up that then we''re going to click on see all settings"},{"start":374.48,"end":379.84,"text":"then you''re going to see where it says undo send and you have send cancellation period five seconds"},{"start":379.84,"end":384.96,"text":"which is what the default is and you can increase that up to 30 seconds so if you know that you''re"},{"start":384.96,"end":390.48,"text":"the type of person that maybe hits send a little too quick you can change that up 30 seconds and"},{"start":390.48,"end":394.48,"text":"i''ll keep that little window on screen for 30 seconds so if you decide you want to change it"},{"start":394.56,"end":401.2,"text":"you have that option to undo that there all right let''s talk about the emails in your inbox if you''ve"},{"start":401.2,"end":406.72,"text":"just set this up you may not have as many emails in there but if you''re have an email account for"},{"start":406.72,"end":411.68,"text":"a while it''ll look something like this this up here shows you that we''re looking at the inbox"},{"start":411.68,"end":417.84,"text":"and we have 566 unread messages but what you could do is you could see the emails that come in in"},{"start":417.84,"end":423.68,"text":"bold mean i haven''t read them yet so you go through there and click on the ones that you haven''t read"},{"start":423.68,"end":429.36,"text":"now when you click on the email it brings up the email here and then you could read it do whatever"},{"start":429.36,"end":434.64,"text":"you need to in the email and then down below you can reply if you need to just say something which"},{"start":434.64,"end":440.48,"text":"is going to create a thread replying to that same email now this from google says no reply so i can''t"},{"start":440.48,"end":445.6,"text":"do that or you could forward this so maybe this concerns somebody else so you can click on forward"},{"start":445.6,"end":450.88,"text":"it''ll take this email and it''ll send it to another person if you just add their email in there"},{"start":450.96,"end":456.24,"text":"so click delete there now let''s say once you''re done reading this you don''t have any more use for"},{"start":456.24,"end":463.2,"text":"it up here at the top you could click on delete and it''ll remove that totally from your box now"},{"start":463.2,"end":469.12,"text":"let''s say you have an email here like this one that i previously read and i go oh you know what i"},{"start":469.68,"end":475.52,"text":"i want to remember to do something with that you could go over here and you could scroll over to"},{"start":475.52,"end":480.72,"text":"this little envelope you see it says mark as unread so you click on that and it treats it just"},{"start":480.72,"end":486.32,"text":"like an unread message so that''ll remind me i need to do something with that again later you could"},{"start":486.32,"end":491.84,"text":"click on multiple emails if you want to click on all of those and then you appear at the top you"},{"start":491.84,"end":498,"text":"can click on delete and get rid of those you could even address any of the ones that have been unread"},{"start":498.72,"end":504.08,"text":"and it''ll only select the ones that are unread you could do multitask with those you can move those"},{"start":504.08,"end":509.2,"text":"to another folder and delete them whatever you want to do now a couple other settings here is"},{"start":509.2,"end":514.64,"text":"we''re going to click on the gear icon here and you could see you have a couple of different settings"},{"start":515.2,"end":519.6,"text":"for defending on how you want it and this is all about how this is displayed so you could change"},{"start":519.6,"end":524.32,"text":"the default right now it''s on the default view which gives you a little preview what the email is"},{"start":524.88,"end":531.6,"text":"you could click on comfortable which gives a little bit more view or compact which kind of"},{"start":531.68,"end":535.92,"text":"shrinks that down even more so if you want to get more emails on the screen at one time you could"},{"start":535.92,"end":542,"text":"go to that i like just sort of the default view you could change your themes so you could change"},{"start":542,"end":546.96,"text":"what this background view again it''s just a personal preference to what you want it to look like"},{"start":546.96,"end":553.04,"text":"maybe i want some of these i like the chess pieces there in the background okay then you could have"},{"start":553.04,"end":559.36,"text":"how it lists the inbox if you want the default or you want the important first or all your unread"},{"start":559.44,"end":565.52,"text":"messages up at the top however you want to organize that depending on your preference i like having"},{"start":565.52,"end":572.08,"text":"just based on the date and time and then you have your reading panel so you could have no split or"},{"start":572.08,"end":576.96,"text":"you could have right to the inbox okay in order to switch to that you got to reload it so we''re"},{"start":576.96,"end":582.64,"text":"going to have that reload and what this does is it brings up so you could have your list of emails"},{"start":582.64,"end":588.24,"text":"here and you could have your email to be read over on this screen so you kind of go through your"},{"start":588.24,"end":595.28,"text":"emails pretty quick that way and then you also have conversation view okay which is basically it"},{"start":595.28,"end":601.68,"text":"groups all of your emails together that are in a thread or if you have replied to an email rather"},{"start":601.68,"end":606.64,"text":"than having that show up as individual emails it''ll have that all as one i always like turning that on"},{"start":606.64,"end":612.32,"text":"because i like having any conversations that are back and forth just treat that as one email one"},{"start":612.32,"end":618.4,"text":"of the other things that you''ll want to see is let''s say you''re searching for an email that you"},{"start":618.4,"end":626.32,"text":"remember getting maybe there was a sale on something so you could click on sale and click there and it''ll"},{"start":626.32,"end":632.64,"text":"bring up any emails that mention sale in there so you can find old emails that way all right now"},{"start":632.64,"end":638.96,"text":"let''s talk a little bit about organizing your emails okay so across the top here you can see"},{"start":639.92,"end":645.68,"text":"that google does some automatic organizations so you can see it kind of drops all the promotions"},{"start":645.68,"end":652.4,"text":"in here it takes the socials and put some in here updates so it does some of that for you already"},{"start":652.4,"end":657.04,"text":"but let''s say you want to organize them even a little bit further and i highly recommend this"},{"start":657.04,"end":662.16,"text":"just to kind of keep your inbox from looking like this where it''s just a bunch of random emails"},{"start":662.16,"end":667.68,"text":"all in one place so you see you have labels here so if you click on the plus button you can create"},{"start":667.76,"end":677.2,"text":"a label and let''s say i want to create one for amazon okay i want to keep all my amazon emails in"},{"start":677.2,"end":683.12,"text":"one account you could organize them further by nesting them under into subcategories we''re not"},{"start":683.12,"end":688.24,"text":"going to worry about that for now but we''re just going to create that so now you have an amazon"},{"start":688.24,"end":694.64,"text":"you see here up at the top we have three amazon emails i''m just going to click on all of those"},{"start":695.44,"end":702.4,"text":"and then when you click and hold on those you drag those three conversations over into the amazon"},{"start":702.4,"end":709.52,"text":"box now when we open that up it now has our amazon emails in there so i think this is a really good"},{"start":709.52,"end":716.88,"text":"way to kind of just go through and organize your emails that way you could create another label that''s"},{"start":717.44,"end":723.52,"text":"needs attention so these are things that i want to do later that i don''t want to do right now so"},{"start":723.6,"end":732.32,"text":"you could go create and let''s say this about my nas i want to take that email and just put that into"},{"start":732.32,"end":738.08,"text":"needs attention now you can see it has a little one there meaning there''s an unread email in that"},{"start":738.08,"end":744.4,"text":"box so i can later go into it open that up and take the necessary actions that i need to take in"},{"start":744.4,"end":749.12,"text":"that one and so with that you can start organizing your email so they''re all sort of in different"},{"start":749.12,"end":755.12,"text":"boxes so that you can keep track of them easy and all of those are still searchable when you"},{"start":755.12,"end":760.16,"text":"search mail it''s going to search all the boxes so you don''t have to worry about that so with that"},{"start":760.16,"end":765.2,"text":"you are up and running with gmail i hope you found this video helpful and i''ll see you in the next one"}]'::jsonb
