y kind of function so here this is kind of a janky it''s you know numbers usually have commas"},{"start":152.88,"end":158.96,"text":"in here so maybe we want to format this so we can format it and then just you know put a comma in"},{"start":158.96,"end":165.6,"text":"there like this shift enter to run this shift in and run it again boom now we''ve got a comma in there"},{"start":165.6,"end":171.2,"text":"right so anything you want to do with python you can do this so it doesn''t just have to be numbers"},{"start":171.2,"end":177.12,"text":"we can add a last name to the names we''ve got these employees up here so let''s come up here and"},{"start":177.12,"end":184.88,"text":"let''s create a function let''s call it namer we want to pass in x and let''s run some logic let''s say if"},{"start":184.88,"end":195.28,"text":"x equals john then we want to return john elder right else we just want to return the name"},{"start":195.6,"end":202.16,"text":"right shift enter to run this and again we can now come down here and do our thing so minor score"},{"start":202.16,"end":209.68,"text":"df and we want to do this on the employees column and we just want to dot apply and we want to pass"},{"start":209.68,"end":216,"text":"in our namer function boom this one says john elder because it had john in it the rest of them"},{"start":216,"end":221.52,"text":"don''t have john so we just returns the name instead of this we could return you know not important"},{"start":221.92,"end":227.92,"text":"right shift enter to run this boom now we''ve got john elder and the rest of the people are just"},{"start":227.92,"end":233.36,"text":"not important so anything you want to do you can do it so so in these two examples we wrote little"},{"start":233.36,"end":237.36,"text":"functions and we kind of wrote them separately you don''t necessarily have to write them separately"},{"start":237.36,"end":242.64,"text":"you can write them in line right here using a lambda if you''re familiar with python you''re"},{"start":242.64,"end":247.68,"text":"probably familiar with lambdas so we come down here and let''s just do this all in one line so"},{"start":247.68,"end":252.8,"text":"and what do we want to do we want to work this on let''s say salary again right and then just dot"},{"start":252.8,"end":260.32,"text":"apply now inside of here we create a lambda lambd a and again let''s just create a dummy variable"},{"start":260.32,"end":265.52,"text":"called x and what do we want to do with x we just want to go x times a thousand shift enter on this"},{"start":265.52,"end":272.96,"text":"and boom same deal we could you know do the same thing again we could format this guy like this"},{"start":273.92,"end":283.36,"text":"and then put comma d there we go piece of cake we could wrap this whole thing in a pd.data frame"},{"start":284.64,"end":289.44,"text":"it''s like we did earlier all still one line boom now it''s a nice little data frame whatever you"},{"start":289.44,"end":294.08,"text":"want to do here''s how you do it so you know a lot of times if it''s a big function you''re going to"},{"start":294.08,"end":297.68,"text":"want to write you''re going to do it separately like this you wouldn''t want to put all of this in one"},{"start":297.68,"end":302.48,"text":"line right but if you''re just doing some little thing like formatting your numbers or adding"},{"start":302.96,"end":307.04,"text":"commas in there or something like that using a lambda might make sense and it''s pretty simple to"},{"start":307.04,"end":311.04,"text":"do that so that is the apply function what do you guys think pretty powerful right i mean you"},{"start":311.04,"end":316.08,"text":"could do absolutely anything with this and it''s just as easy as dot apply naming the function"},{"start":316.08,"end":319.92,"text":"and there you go so that''s all for this video if you like to be sure to smash like button below"},{"start":319.92,"end":323.44,"text":"subscribe to the channel give me a thumbs up for the youtube algorithm and check out code me.com"},{"start":323.44,"end":328.16,"text":"we can use coupon code youtube 50 to get 50 off membership so that''s access to all my courses"},{"start":328.16,"end":332.4,"text":"over 50 courses thousands of videos in the pds of all my best selling clinic books join over 150"},{"start":332.48,"end":335.92,"text":"thousand students learn to code just like you my name is john elder from coding me dot com and i''ll"},{"start":335.92,"end":338.64,"text":"see you in the next video"}]'::jsonb
